WEBVTT

00:04:29.585 --> 00:04:36.385
That's an astonishing 35 million homes
globally, every year.

00:04:37.641 --> 00:04:39.387
And in Australia alone,

00:04:39.411 --> 00:04:43.902
we have a shortfall of 250,000 dwellings.

00:04:44.768 --> 00:04:47.934
And in addition to that,

00:04:47.958 --> 00:04:53.799
we have 190,000 families
on the assisted-housing wait list;

00:04:54.481 --> 00:04:57.847
families in need of a home.

00:04:59.615 --> 00:05:02.687
Between now and 2050,